{"tid":422678,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[屋漏兼夜雨]逃生滑梯突放出充氣 香港快運乘客受阻1粒鐘","createTime":"2017-10-03T09:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T09:43:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"250b98a3e1ca34f4fcabbb35117d0173985ff29c","tid":422678,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"陰公豬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171003/57285598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171003%2F57285598&d=UZAdTXUFKOLvNuBFb7Lfs4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=b2c706a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171003%2F57285598&h=f74c166b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171003/57285598</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1507011983_cc9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1507011983_cc9b.jpg&h=b5301ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 香港快運航空一班編號UO870的客機，在停機坪準備期間，機身的救生梯突然放下並充氣。目擊者稱，險些擊中在場上貨的工人。最後航空公司要安排另一航機載客，旅客行程受阻約1小時。<br />\n<br />\n該班編號UO870的航機，原定上午11時20起飛往東京。目擊者張先生稱，早上10時28分左右，當時有工人上貨，突然「嘭」一聲響，「救生梯彈咗出嚟，仲吹漲咗，差啲整到班工人。後來見到機艙內走出兩個航空公司既人。」結果航空公司要安排另一航機接載乘客，而根據機管局的網頁，UO870於中午12時31分啟航，比預期延誤超過1小時。<br />\n<br />\n機管局稱，今早10時半左右，收到香港快運通知，一架準備飛往東京的航班，在停泊於207號閘口期間，其逃生氣墊滑梯彈出，當時並無乘客，機場運作不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n就此事件，本報正向航空公司查詢。"},{"pid":"1702a3aef16ca08219e96933de9fc9f64be64845","tid":422678,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"可能有人多手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191f0257c6f08b81c3e873923f5c6a9c4b8ddede","tid":422678,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"執未"},{"pid":"37733055b2138d35b764e87014e989465ac146ed","tid":422678,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"是是旦旦飛得起咪得, 咁多要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924353f1266ac17f21f7951684aab48be6457743","tid":422678,"uid":10008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"好彩依家有機多冇人渣先可以即換機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係幾日後先飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}